name: unary_bajyra
hlo:

  func.func public @main(%arg0: tensor<3x3xf32>) -> (tensor<3x3xf32> {jax.result_info = "result"}) {
    %0 = stablehlo.abs %arg0 : tensor<3x3xf32>
    %cst = stablehlo.constant dense<9.99999997E-7> : tensor<f32>
